A query can have multiple criterion, and a criteria consists of a type (clinical, genomic, image, etc), name/value, and a comparator (>, <. eq, in...), so an example would be Smoking Status = True, where "Smoking Status" is the name, "True" is the value, and "=" is the comparator, and in this case it would be of clinical type.
